        <item>
            <title>美研可穿戴血壓計大小如郵票，非入侵技術超聲波隨時量血壓</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/05/researchers-develop-wearable-patch-that-monitors-blood-pressure-anywhere/life-tech/health/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=researchers-develop-wearable-patch-that-monitors-blood-pressure-anywhere</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/12/05/researchers-develop-wearable-patch-that-monitors-blood-pressure-anywhere/life-tech/health/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 10:00:17 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[健康]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[美國研究]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[血壓計]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[超聲波]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1279421</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>美國研究團隊宣佈成功開發一款超聲波貼片，能以非入侵性方式持續監測人體血壓。目前相關研究論文已刊登在權威科學期刊《Nature（自然）》，貼片已收集逾百名患者臨牀測試數據，有望為心血管健康監測帶來新突破。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279423" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/wearableultrasoundpa-1-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/wearableultrasoundpa-1-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/wearableultrasoundpa-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://scitechdaily.com/researchers-develop-wearable-patch-that-monitors-blood-pressure-anywhere/">Sci Tech Daily</a></p><p>美國加州大學聖地牙哥分校（(University of California San Diego，UC San Diego）在權威學術期刊《Nature》發表研究論文，表示成功開發一款超聲波貼片，具有柔軟且可拉伸的特性，能以非入侵性方式持續監測人體血壓。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279430" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120531933-694x564.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="564" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120531933-694x564.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024120531933.jpg 1107w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px;">▲島橋結構使貼片具有柔軟且可拉伸的特性<br />
圖片來源：</span><a style="text-align: center; font-size: 16px;" href="https://today.ucsd.edu/story/wearable_ultrasound_patch_monitors_blood_pressure_deep_inside_body">UC San Diego</a></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279426" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/saizhouholdingultras-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/saizhouholdingultras-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/saizhouholdingultras.jpg 777w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲UC San Diego 研發團隊成員之一，圖片來源：<a href="https://scitechdaily.com/researchers-develop-wearable-patch-that-monitors-blood-pressure-anywhere/">Sci Tech Daily</a></p><p>這款貼片大小與郵票相若，使用方式亦與郵票相近，用家可以將貼片貼在前臂，能夠實時提供精確的深層組織血壓讀數。貼片矽膠彈性體製成，使用小型電壓感測器發送和接收超聲波，以追蹤血管直徑的變化，進而轉換為血壓數值。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279427" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/wearableultrasoundpa-2-694x363.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="363" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/wearableultrasoundpa-2-694x363.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/wearableultrasoundpa-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://scitechdaily.com/researchers-develop-wearable-patch-that-monitors-blood-pressure-anywhere/">Sci Tech Daily</a></p><p>傳統袖帶式血壓計每次只可提供單次血壓值，無法紀錄血壓詳細波動資訊，而 SC San Diego 最新研發的貼片可量度連續的血壓波形數據，紀錄血壓波動的詳細趨勢。據外媒報道，貼片在臨牀測試的表現與傳統袖帶式血壓計和動脈導管相當。動脈導管數據雖然精準，但需要刺穿患者皮膚，具有侵入性，量度時可能引起不適，並限制患者的活動，反觀貼片則無須刺穿患者皮膚，同時亦不會限制患者活動，另外亦可長時間測量患者血壓變化。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279433" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/maxresdefault-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/maxresdefault-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/maxresdefault-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲傳統袖帶式血壓計，圖片來源：<a href="https://i.ytimg.com/vi/M_LpuQJxm3A/maxresdefault.jpg">YouTube</a></p><p>UC San Diego 研究人員收集了 117 名參與測試病患的數據，包括在日常活動和不同姿勢下的血壓監測，結果證實了貼片的安全性比動脈導管更高，而且準確性與傳統量度血壓方式（袖帶式血壓計、動脈導管）非常一致，技術有望提升臨牀和家庭環境心血管健康監測精準度，為患者和醫護人員提供更便捷的血壓監測工具。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1279424" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/bloodpressurepatchon-694x254.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="254" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/bloodpressurepatchon-694x254.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/bloodpressurepatchon.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://today.ucsd.edu/story/wearable_ultrasound_patch_monitors_blood_pressure_deep_inside_body">UC San Diego</a></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://scitechdaily.com/researchers-develop-wearable-patch-that-monitors-blood-pressure-anywhere/">Sci Tech Daily</a>、<a href="https://today.ucsd.edu/story/wearable_ultrasound_patch_monitors_blood_pressure_deep_inside_body">UC San Diego</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
